Package com.owlike.genson.reflect

This package contains the core api providing databinding support for complex objects.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
BeanDescriptorProvider Interface implemented by classes who want to provide BeanDescriptor instances for the specified type.
BeanMutatorAccessorResolver BeanMutatorAccessorResolver interface must be implemented by class who want to resolve mutators (fields or methods that allow you to modify a property), accessors (fields or methods that allow you to retrieve the value of a property) and creators (constructors or static methods that allow you to create objects).
PropertyNameResolver This interface is intended to be implemented by classes who want to change the way genson does name resolution.
 

Class Summary
AbstractBeanDescriptorProvider Abstract implementation of BeanDescriptorProvider applying the template pattern.
ASMCreatorParameterNameResolver This class uses ASM library to resolve method and constructor parameter names from debug symbols generated during compilation.
BaseBeanDescriptorProvider Standard implementation of AbstractBeanDescriptorProvider that uses BeanMutatorAccessorResolver and PropertyNameResolver.

BeanViewDescriptorProvider This class constructs BeanDescriptor for the BeanView mechanism.
BeanViewDescriptorProvider.BeanViewMutatorAccessorResolver

PropertyMutator.FieldMutator<T,P>

PropertyNameResolver.CompositePropertyNameResolver  
PropertyNameResolver.ConventionalBeanPropertyNameResolver  
TypeUtil This class is mainly intended for internal use, however you are free to use it.
VisibilityFilter This class is used as filter for properties discovery.
